I was born in Piano di Sotto,

23:25.560 --> 23:27.200
Trapani province, Sicily.

23:27.960 --> 23:30.520
I'm a fisherman and a sailor.

23:31.240 --> 23:34.000
An islander,
just like me, hmm?

23:34.600 --> 23:36.960
I knew
we would understand each other.

23:39.120 --> 23:41.400
Now... So...

23:41.400 --> 23:43.440
In the boat,
besides two kilos of cocaine,

23:43.440 --> 23:45.760
we found passports with different names
and fake documents.

23:45.760 --> 23:47.440
Was he travelling alone?

23:47.440 --> 23:48.680
Yes and no, detective.

23:50.280 --> 23:51.120
Yes or no?

23:51.120 --> 23:52.480
When we questioned him,

23:52.480 --> 23:55.520
he said "<i>da solo</i>" in Italian.

23:55.520 --> 23:58.400
And we couldn't understand
if he meant he was traveling alone,

23:58.960 --> 24:00.720
or whether he liked his coffee black.

24:06.120 --> 24:09.120
