He studied three months in Bologna.

24:22.160 --> 24:23.640
- To the left. Yes.
- In here?

24:24.240 --> 24:26.320
You leave Venezuela

24:26.320 --> 24:28.400
with a sailboat loaded with cocaine,

24:28.400 --> 24:30.080
headed for the Canary Islands.

24:30.640 --> 24:31.920
