how much crap did you bring,

24:47.760 --> 24:49.080
Mr. Francesco?

25:04.200 --> 25:05.760
Five hundred kilos?

25:12.360 --> 25:14.240
Maybe a little less.

25:15.960 --> 25:18.640
So,
we already found everything.

25:20.280 --> 25:21.920
Only crumbs
left for the fish...

25:21.920 --> 25:23.720
Where's the info on the boat?

25:30.560 --> 25:33.080
Would you risk crossing the Atlantic
on an almost-empty boat

25:33.080 --> 25:35.040
