26:03.880 --> 26:05.440
It's to disguise the fish smell.

26:06.040 --> 26:07.360
I'm going to bed.

26:08.200 --> 26:10.320
- Don't waste water.
- Good night.

26:29.200 --> 26:30.280
- Good evening.
- Ah.

26:31.480 --> 26:33.280
- You can't go in.
- Why not?

26:33.280 --> 26:34.640
The flip-flops.

26:34.640 --> 26:35.720
I'll be back, okay?

26:36.480 --> 26:37.320
Okay.

26:37.960 --> 26:39.080
