27:07.640 --> 27:08.720
Sit here.

27:11.560 --> 27:12.400
What's up?

27:13.360 --> 27:14.880
You like those boots? Huh?

27:16.960 --> 27:19.120
- I appreciate it.
- They were my grandfather's.

27:20.160 --> 27:21.160
Yeah.

27:21.160 --> 27:23.400
His dead body was warm in the coffin
when I grabbed 'em.

27:25.080 --> 27:26.760
Those boots were his favorite.

27:30.400 --> 27:32.080
- Ian.
- Eduardo.

27:36.240 --> 27:37.840
Do you have more?

27:38.880 --> 27:40.000
Huh?

27:40.920 --> 27:44.400
Do you have more of those little baggies
Sílvia got for me?

27:51.920 --> 27:54.480
Whoa, oh, oh! Come on.
What, are you in pre-school, dude?

27:56.280 --> 27:58.360
Let's go. Inside, come on.

28:05.040 --> 28:08.280
- You have a lot of this one, right?
- Getting more won't be a problem.

28:11.160 --> 28:13.640
