28:36.160 --> 28:37.080
What?

28:43.360 --> 28:45.880
You don't want to fuck me, right? Huh?

28:45.880 --> 28:48.040
You came here
to fucking fuck me, motherfucker?

28:48.040 --> 28:49.040
- No, no.
- Huh?

28:49.040 --> 28:51.400
