28:53.160 --> 28:54.880
Uh-huh.

28:56.440 --> 28:59.040
Okay.

28:59.040 --> 29:01.720
- Tomorrow. Tomorrow.
- Tomorrow?

29:02.720 --> 29:04.480
Two. Hmm?

29:05.120 --> 29:06.320
- Two kilos?
- Shhh.

29:06.320 --> 29:07.280
