29:43.200 --> 29:45.240
- I mean it. Get something tribal.
- Please don't start.

29:45.240 --> 29:47.120
- You wanna get girls or what?
- Shut your mouth.

29:47.120 --> 29:48.760
- I just sold two kilos.
- You sold to Ian?

29:48.760 --> 29:50.120
He held his fingers up like this.

29:50.120 --> 29:51.320
- That's two kilos.
- Two kilos?

29:51.320 --> 29:53.000
Seriously, man, that's awesome!

29:53.880 --> 29:57.240
Hey, girl, pretty face!
So it's two shots of vodka with melon.

29:57.240 --> 30:00.000
The entrepreneur here is paying.

30:03.360 --> 30:05.400
