- Huh?

30:06.360 --> 30:07.480
For Ian's order?

30:08.120 --> 30:09.120
Yeah, okay.

30:11.960 --> 30:13.920
But you can show up there
whenever you want.

30:24.080 --> 30:26.160
Shut up!

30:26.160 --> 30:27.880
- No bullshit, all right?
- Just some advice.

30:27.880 --> 30:29.240
