33:57.080 --> 33:58.520
Wait a minute. You--

34:00.400 --> 34:03.000
Wait a second. You're Rafael Medeiros?

34:03.000 --> 34:05.760
Yes. Yes, I am.

34:05.760 --> 34:08.040
Come in, Rafael!

34:08.040 --> 34:10.360
Rafael Medeiros in my house!

34:11.640 --> 34:15.640
Guys! Look, a celebrity is gracing us
with his presence.

34:15.640 --> 34:18.320
Santa Clara, number nine jersey,
in '97-'98 season.

34:18.320 --> 34:20.320
Excuse me,
is Bruna outside or is she--

34:20.320 --> 34:21.680
Uh, she must be asleep.

34:21.680 --> 34:23.760
Rafael, what do you want to eat?
Pork belly?

34:23.760 --> 34:26.000
I have some linguiça from Flores.

34:26.000 --> 34:27.280
Where's the bathroom?

34:27.280 --> 34:30.320
It seems like I'm not the only one
who doesn't know anyone here.

34:32.360 --> 34:33.520
Yeah.

34:53.200 --> 34:55.120
You gotta be kidding me.

35:09.920 --> 35:11.000
Fuck this.

35:20.200 --> 35:21.480
Fuck me!

35:25.920 --> 35:27.440
It's the only cold drink I could find.

35:27.440 --> 35:29.720
