35:56.520 --> 35:59.600
See if you can get a mop or something?
'Cause I spilled this shit everywhere.

35:59.600 --> 36:01.640
Come on, Rafael,
there are people waiting. Hurry.

36:01.640 --> 36:03.960
- It's all over the place.
- Shit.

36:03.960 --> 36:05.800
Come on,
there are people waiting.

36:05.800 --> 36:06.720
Bro!

36:07.400 --> 36:08.240
Thanks.

36:11.880 --> 36:13.480
You forgot your manners.

36:13.480 --> 36:15.560
Fuck, what a fucking nightmare.

36:19.080 --> 36:20.320
Fucking shit!

36:29.640 --> 36:31.320
Okay, okay.

36:35.840 --> 36:37.200
All yours.

36:47.840 --> 36:50.000
It was a goal
for the ages, right?

36:50.000 --> 36:52.960
For a second, I thought
Luz Stadium was coming down.

36:52.960 --> 36:56.120
- We have to leave, man. Come on.
- You're going? But you haven't eaten yet.

36:58.440 --> 37:00.680
Dad, we're going to the movies
and we're late, so...

37:02.520 --> 37:04.920
- Come on, let's leave.
- What are you doing? Bruna's here!

37:04.920 --> 37:07.600
We're at a cops' barbecue, fuckhead.
Let's go.

37:09.000 --> 37:11.440
- Have you lost your fucking mind?
- Hey, hey, guys!

37:16.240 --> 37:17.960
You're not leaving empty-handed.

37:19.160 --> 37:20.880
Here. Take these linguiças with you.

37:23.360 --> 37:25.800
- Thank you.
- Hold up. I'll need that Tupperware back.

37:25.800 --> 37:28.560
- I'll get it when I'm in Rabo de Peixe.
- Okay, sounds good.

37:30.760 --> 37:33.080
Rafael Medeiros, jersey number nine.

37:46.480 --> 37:48.160
I'm sorry, okay? I'm sorry! I fell asleep.

37:48.160 --> 37:51.280
Save it! Your dad is a cop,
and you didn't think to tell us?

37:51.280 --> 37:53.280
Led us to the sharks
so we can be ripped apart?

37:53.280 --> 37:54.800
Tell your boyfriend no deal, Bruna.

37:54.800 --> 37:56.400
Oh, come on, Eduardo, wait!

37:56.400 --> 37:57.680
What the fuck?

37:57.680 --> 37:58.880
Fuck!

37:59.520 --> 38:00.440
Fuckers!

38:01.280 --> 38:02.120
Fuck!

38:04.160 --> 38:05.480
Fuck you, asshole!

38:08.000 --> 38:09.600
Shit!

38:09.600 --> 38:12.400
Are you feeling
this adrenaline, bro?

38:13.600 --> 38:16.120
Huh? We were in a fucking cop's house,
carrying coke!

38:16.120 --> 38:18.480
