39:11.800 --> 39:14.200
Morning walk in Rabo de Peixe.

39:14.800 --> 39:16.760
Exactly what I needed on a Sunday morning.

39:16.760 --> 39:17.680
Right now?

39:17.680 --> 39:19.600
We're going in strong.

39:25.040 --> 39:27.160
