40:19.360 --> 40:20.800
Come on!

40:22.840 --> 40:23.680
Hello?

40:23.680 --> 40:26.720
<i>Sílvia, the judiciary police
are coming to raid Rabo de Peixe.</i>

40:26.720 --> 40:27.640
Fuck.

40:52.000 --> 40:54.360
