45:06.280 --> 45:07.480
Judge's orders.

45:17.520 --> 45:18.600
Let's go, let's go!

45:22.040 --> 45:22.920
Fuck!

45:22.920 --> 45:23.960
Detective Banha!

45:25.040 --> 45:26.960
We have to let them all go.

45:26.960 --> 45:28.520
Told you!

45:28.520 --> 45:31.280
You heard the lady!
Come on, come on, release me!

45:31.280 --> 45:34.000
Ha! We're free to go, motherfuckers!

45:34.760 --> 45:36.240
Let's get out of here, huh?

45:37.720 --> 45:38.760
Ah...

