47:00.160 --> 47:01.080
Right here.

47:06.360 --> 47:07.440
Come on.

47:14.920 --> 47:16.280
Pull!

47:18.800 --> 47:21.040
It's there. It's there!

47:25.200 --> 47:26.400
No, like this.

47:27.040 --> 47:29.640
We are the real Ribeira Grande,
ladies and gentlemen!

47:29.640 --> 47:33.160
Fuck yeah, motherfuckers!

47:36.000 --> 47:38.760
It's God's will!
Never forget that, okay, Rafael?

47:39.440 --> 47:40.360
God's will.

47:52.880 --> 47:55.160
<i>After winning
the cocaine lottery,</i>

47:55.680 --> 47:57.680
<i>and the miracle of escaping the police,</i>

47:58.200 --> 47:59.120
<i>now, tell me,</i>

48:00.160 --> 48:04.000
<i>why wouldn't Eduardo believe
that, for the first time in his life,</i>

48:04.000 --> 48:05.520
<i>God was on his side?</i>

48:30.000 --> 48:31.720
<i>But on these islands,</i>

48:31.720 --> 48:34.000
<i>the sun never shines for long.</i>

48:35.240 --> 48:38.160
<i>Some unfortunates already have
their destiny traced</i>

48:38.160 --> 48:39.680
